Package org.neo4j.server.security.systemgraph

Class KnownSystemComponentVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.server.security.systemgraph.KnownSystemComponentVersion
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    KnownCommunitySecurityComponentVersion
    public abstract class KnownSystemComponentVersion
extends Object
    Version of a system graph component. Components that due to breaking schema changes requires migrations also needs versions. Each component has its own version scheme starting at 0 and increasing each release with breaking changes. The versions should be on the format [component]Version_[versionNbr]_[neo4jRelease]. The version schemes are described in ComponentVersion.
